      "review_summary": "The PR replaces OpenAI Batch status JSON, ChatGPT OAuth token-body, and Realtime client-secret JSON response reads with bounded response-reader helpers.\n\nPR surface: Source +10. Total +10 across 3 files.\n\nReproducibility: no. live end-to-end reproduction was established, but source inspection gives a clear reproduction path: current main uses unbounded success-body reads in Batch status, OAuth token exchange, and Realtime client-secret parsing. The shared bounded-reader tests prove the proposed primitive cancels oversized streams.",
      "review_followup": "- [P1] Human review is needed because the contributor must provide changed-path real behavior proof and maintainers must accept or adjust the OAuth cap; automation cannot supply that proof for them.",
